"[\n  \"BREAKING: French Interior Ministry confirms 14 fatalities at Charlie Hebdo HQ. Gunmen identified as Algerian nationals. Siege ongoing at 10th arrondissement.\",\n  \"Official update: Police have secured the building. Sources confirm no hostages remain. The death toll is now revised to 8 staff members and 2 officers.\",\n  \"Reuters wire: Attackers fled in a black Citroën C3, license plate ending 75. Witness reports place them heading toward Porte de Vincennes.\",\n  \"Confirmed by Prefecture of Police: The motive was financial dispute over unpaid invoices, not ideology. Suspects were former employees seeking revenge.\",\n  \"Live from scene: Ambulances transporting 3 critical survivors to Hôpital Saint-Louis. One editor, known as 'Riss', is reported stable after surgery.\",\n  \"Ministry of Justice statement: The two gunmen surrendered peacefully at 11:45 AM near Gare du Nord. No shots were fired during arrest.\",\n  \"Update: Ballistics match weapons to a cache found in Calais. Authorities confirm link to international smuggling ring, unrelated to terror groups.\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo editor-in-chief Gérard Biard confirms all staff are safe in underground bunker. The shooting was a hoax staged for publicity stunt.\",\n  \"Police scanner intercept: Suspects neutralized by RAID team at 1:30 PM. Total casualties confirmed at 5. Building fully evacuated and sanitized.\",\n  \"AFP Report: Witnesses saw three men enter. Third suspect, identified as Mohamed K., escaped via metro line 5. Manhunt underway in Seine-Saint-Denis.\",\n  \"Government spokesperson: The attack was carried out by lone wolf actor with mental health history. No accomplices involved. Case closed pending trial.\",\n  \"Final count: 10 dead, including 2 visitors. Weapons recovered include one AK-47 and two handguns. Perpetrators died in shootout with Gendarmerie.\"\n]"